---
title: Sweet Potato and Bacon Orzo with Spinach
description: Looking for a tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Sweet Potato Orzo in just 20 minutes for a balanced and tasty dinnertime.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/superquick-butternut-orxo-9cdf4f64-7f09726a.jpg
